♫ Both honored and disgraced, tasting the warmth and cold,
making it hard finding a place to return ♫

13
00:01:30,067 --> 00:01:33,133
[Episode 8]

14
00:01:35,600 --> 00:01:39,040
If you still care for our poor daughter,

15
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:42,820
then from today onwards, you must listen to me.

16
00:01:42,820 --> 00:01:44,980
You can never come back,

17
00:01:44,980 --> 00:01:47,199
and never think about Dao Baifeng.

18
00:01:47,199 --> 00:01:48,559
It's not that I don't want to,

19
00:01:48,559 --> 00:01:49,999
but I'm the Prince Zhennan of Dali Kingdom,

20
00:01:49,999 --> 00:01:51,960
I hold the reins of power in both civil and military affairs.

21
00:01:51,960 --> 00:01:54,340
I can't just leave.

22
00:01:54,340 --> 00:01:57,120
You said that eighteen years ago,

23
00:01:57,120 --> 00:02:00,180
and yet eighteen years later, you say the same thing.

24
00:02:00,180 --> 00:02:02,279
Duan Zhengchun, Duan Zhengchun,

25
00:02:02,279 --> 00:02:05,660
you're a heartless man.

26
00:02:05,660 --> 00:02:07,660
I hate you.

27
00:02:07,660 --> 00:02:13,060
Timing and Subtitles brought to you by ⚔️Martial Arts Team ⚔️@Viki.com

28
00:02:13,060 --> 00:02:15,720
You have held the title of prince for over a decade now.

29
00:02:15,720 --> 00:02:17,960
Why can't you let it go?

30
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:20,079
Look at our precious daughter.

31
00:02:20,079 --> 00:02:24,840
Don't you feel sorry for her?

32
00:02:24,840 --> 00:02:26,460
All right.

33
00:02:27,040 --> 00:02:29,140
I'll go with you.

34
00:02:29,140 --> 00:02:31,100
Senior Sister!

35
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:35,459
Senior Sister! You have been fooled by him again.

36
00:02:35,459 --> 00:02:36,959
He is going to fool with you for some days

37
00:02:36,959 --> 00:02:39,500
and then he'll return to his place as the prince again.

38
00:02:39,500 --> 00:02:41,320
Baobao?

39
00:02:44,600 --> 00:02:47,720
Baobao, what a surprise.

40
00:02:47,720 --> 00:02:50,279
Why are you here? How are you?

41
00:02:50,279 --> 00:02:52,000
You still remember me.

42
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:53,880
Assassins!

43
00:02:54,480 --> 00:02:56,140
Get out of the way!

44
00:02:58,560 --> 00:03:00,240
Father.

45
00:03:03,480 --> 00:03:05,580
Duan!

46
00:03:05,580 --> 00:03:07,299
Duan, are you all right?

47
00:03:07,299 --> 00:03:11,260
Little Sister, from now on, you have to call me brother.

48
00:03:11,260 --> 00:03:15,020
Loving each other as siblings is also fine.

49
00:03:15,020 --> 00:03:16,620
No.

50
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:20,020
I don't believe it.

51
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:23,980
You are the first man who has ever seen my face.

52
00:03:23,980 --> 00:03:26,240
I've sworn.

53
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,799
I've sworn. I don't believe it!

54
00:03:27,799 --> 00:03:29,719
- Wan'er!
- I don't believe it!

55
00:03:29,719 --> 00:03:31,720
- Wan'er come back!
- Hong Mian.

56
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:38,160
Let my son go now!

57
00:03:38,160 --> 00:03:40,900
He is going back with me as my apprentice.

58
00:03:44,831 --> 00:03:48,499
Order your men to retreat immediately!

59
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:55,480
Fall back!

60
00:03:59,320 --> 00:04:01,000
Let's go!

61
00:04:30,535 --> 00:04:32,919
Do you want to keep him alive or not?

62
00:04:32,919 --> 00:04:34,859
He was wounded by a poison arrow and is seriously injured.

63
00:04:34,859 --> 00:04:38,524
Let him go first. We can talk everything out.

64
00:04:40,520 --> 00:04:43,720
Follow my boss to Wanjie Valley to talk then!

65
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:45,380
Yu'er!

66
00:04:47,440 --> 00:04:49,020
Yu'er!

67
00:04:50,640 --> 00:04:54,400
Duan Zhengchun, shall we have a battle today?

68
00:04:54,400 --> 00:04:57,200
Baobao, are you putting me in a difficult position, too?

69
00:04:57,200 --> 00:04:59,520
What nonsense are you talking about?

70
00:04:59,520 --> 00:05:01,320
Listen!

71
00:05:01,320 --> 00:05:04,776
I am the wife of Zhong Wanchou, the Chief of Wanjie Valley.

72
00:05:06,460 --> 00:05:09,359
Baobao, I've been missing you a lot lately.

73
00:05:09,359 --> 00:05:11,640
How have you been all these years?

74
00:05:11,640 --> 00:05:15,280
I'm fine without you.

75
00:05:16,300 --> 00:05:17,920
Junior Sister!

76
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:22,320
Please excuse me.

77
00:05:25,700 --> 00:05:28,099
Duan Zhengchun, you have bullied us.

78
00:05:28,099 --> 00:05:30,339
I sincerely apologize to the both of you.

79
00:05:30,339 --> 00:05:32,619
Who wants your apology? Let us go now!

80
00:05:32,619 --> 00:05:35,019
Hong Mian, calm down.

81
00:05:35,019 --> 00:05:36,819
You have to believe what I just said.

82
00:05:36,819 --> 00:05:40,679
Senior Sister, this guy is an expert in sweet-talking people.

83
00:05:40,679 --> 00:05:42,660
Don't believe anything he says.

84
00:05:42,660 --> 00:05:45,059
Then, Baobao, I'd like to ask you.

85
00:05:45,059 --> 00:05:47,339
What kind of man did you marry?

86
00:05:47,339 --> 00:05:51,250
My husband, he's ugly, has a bad temper,

87
00:05:51,250 --> 00:05:52,959
his martial arts skills are nothing like you,

88
00:05:52,959 --> 00:05:55,200
don't even mention your wealth and status.

89
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:58,579
However, he loves me wholeheartedly,

90
00:05:58,579 --> 00:06:01,019
and I love him with all my heart and soul, too.

91
00:06:01,019 --> 00:06:02,880
If I were to fail him,

92
00:06:02,881 --> 00:06:06,051
then I, Gan Baobao, shall stand condemned by God,

93
00:06:06,051 --> 00:06:07,659
and would be condemned to eternal suffering.

94
00:06:07,659 --> 00:06:09,860
Don't say such nonsense.

95
00:06:10,840 --> 00:06:13,659
It's me that's not blessed to have you treat me like that.

96
00:06:13,659 --> 00:06:16,000
It's me to blame, I'm not good enough.

97
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:19,319
But... why did both of you take my son captive?

98
00:06:19,319 --> 00:06:22,319
Baobao, where is that Wanjie Valley?

99
00:06:22,319 --> 00:06:25,180
His Majesty the Emperor arrives!

100
00:06:40,240 --> 00:06:42,599
Brother! Don't do this!

101
00:06:42,599 --> 00:06:45,100
Yu'er was held captive.

102
00:06:45,100 --> 00:06:47,400
Wan Li told me everything.

103
00:06:48,100 --> 00:06:52,179
Brother Chun, now that the descendant of the Duan family has fallen into the hands of others,

104
00:06:52,179 --> 00:06:55,880
he must be rescued by his parents and uncle.

105
00:06:55,880 --> 00:06:59,239
If you take both of them as hostages to exchange for your son,

106
00:06:59,239 --> 00:07:02,740
it'll ruin the reputation of the Dali Duan family.

107
00:07:02,740 --> 00:07:04,779
You are a member of the royal family,

108
00:07:04,779 --> 00:07:07,139
how can you act like a night thief?

109
00:07:07,139 --> 00:07:09,240
In three days,

110
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:11,579
someone from the Duan family will get him back from the Wanjie Valley.

111
00:07:11,579 --> 00:07:14,479
Both of you, do as you please.

112
00:07:20,140 --> 00:07:23,480
I have to forget Duan Yu and never think of him again.

113
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:31,100
I was once an orphan without parents,

114
00:07:31,100 --> 00:07:35,940
but now I have a father and a mother,

115
00:07:35,940 --> 00:07:38,600
and a brother too.

116
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:41,280
I should feel happy.

117
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:51,140
Right, all I need is to take a leap,

118
00:07:51,140 --> 00:07:53,620
and I can leave all worries behind.

119
00:08:26,100 --> 00:08:27,800
Who is it?

120
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:33,860
Who's there?

121
00:08:33,860 --> 00:08:35,600
Who?

122
00:08:51,440 --> 00:08:55,780
Senior, was it you who saved me just then?

123
00:09:00,360 --> 00:09:01,619
Who is it?

124
00:09:01,619 --> 00:09:04,519
How dare you pull a trick on me, are you tired of living?

125
00:09:04,519 --> 00:09:08,160
I'm indeed tired of living.

126
00:09:09,040 --> 00:09:10,800
Are you the one talking to me?

127
00:09:10,800 --> 00:09:12,980
Exactly.

128
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:14,919
Are you a ghost?

129
00:09:14,919 --> 00:09:18,539
You're the one who doesn't want to live and wants to be a ghost,

130
00:09:18,539 --> 00:09:21,819
then why are you scared of ghosts?

131
00:09:21,819 --> 00:09:23,099
I'm not afraid of ghosts.

132
00:09:23,099 --> 00:09:26,620
I, Mu Wanqing, fear nothing and no one.

133
00:09:27,280 --> 00:09:29,339
You're afraid of one thing,

134
00:09:29,339 --> 00:09:33,039
you're afraid that your husband

135
00:09:33,039 --> 00:09:36,420
has turned out to be your blood brother.

136
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:39,719
You're a ghost. How dare you speak nonsense to me.

137
00:09:39,719 --> 00:09:40,839
I'll kill you!

138
00:09:40,839 --> 00:09:45,220
You've fallen deeply in love, don't deceive yourself.

139
00:09:45,220 --> 00:09:50,260
I know what's in your mind.

140
00:09:50,260 --> 00:09:54,340
[Overflowing with Evil: Duan Yanqing]
We barely know each other. How do you know what's on my mind?

141
00:09:54,340 --> 00:09:56,539
I have a better idea

142
00:09:56,539 --> 00:10:00,719
to make your blood brother your husband.

143
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:02,820
Do you believe me?

144
00:10:03,800 --> 00:10:07,680
You're not even afraid of death, what else can you be afraid of?

145
00:10:07,680 --> 00:10:09,920
Follow me.

146
00:10:23,280 --> 00:10:26,879
Senior, why do you bring me to Wanjie Valley?

147
00:10:27,660 --> 00:10:30,280
Keep up, little girl.

148
00:10:59,500 --> 00:11:01,280
Go in.

149
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:30,360
Let me out! Open the door!

150
00:11:30,360 --> 00:11:33,920
Sister Wan? Sister Wan!

151
00:11:37,300 --> 00:11:39,600
Why are you here, too?

152
00:11:39,600 --> 00:11:41,100
Duan!

153
00:11:43,140 --> 00:11:44,620
Sister Wan.

154
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:54,900
Sister Wan.

155
00:11:56,540 --> 00:11:58,220
We are siblings,

156
00:11:58,220 --> 00:12:00,320
we can't be like this.

157
00:12:03,180 --> 00:12:04,740
Sister Wan.

158
00:12:09,980 --> 00:12:13,100
Sister Wan. Sister Wan.

159
00:12:14,400 --> 00:12:17,060
This is predestined,

160
00:12:17,060 --> 00:12:19,280
don't be too upset about it.

161
00:12:19,280 --> 00:12:23,840
But... But I am happy to have a sister like you.

162
00:12:23,840 --> 00:12:27,220
I want to be upset, I don't want to be happy.

163
00:12:27,220 --> 00:12:31,579
If you are happy, then you're a man with no conscience!

164
00:12:31,579 --> 00:12:34,640
There's nothing I can do.

165
00:12:34,640 --> 00:12:39,932
If I hadn't met you at the very beginning,

166
00:12:39,932 --> 00:12:41,479
then everything would be fine.

167
00:12:41,480 --> 00:12:44,020
It's not that I want to meet you either.

168
00:12:44,020 --> 00:12:46,119
It was you who came to alarm me.

169
00:12:46,120 --> 00:12:50,040
I wouldn't die even if you didn't alarm me.

170
00:12:50,040 --> 00:12:51,720
It's all your fault.

171
00:12:51,720 --> 00:12:54,540
You caused the death of my Black Rose.

172
00:12:54,540 --> 00:12:56,900
It was you who made my master my mother.

173
00:12:56,900 --> 00:13:00,340
It was you who made your father my father.

174
00:13:00,340 --> 00:13:03,440
It's you who made yourself my brother.

175
00:13:07,780 --> 00:13:10,740
I don't want to! I don't want to! I want nothing!

176
00:13:10,740 --> 00:13:13,100
I was imprisoned here because of you!

177
00:13:13,100 --> 00:13:15,500
I want to go out!

178
00:13:15,500 --> 00:13:16,820
Sister Wan.

179
00:13:17,760 --> 00:13:19,820
Yes, it's all my fault.

180
00:13:19,820 --> 00:13:22,440
Please don't be sad anymore.

181
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:25,459
Let's think of a way to get out of here, okay?

182
00:13:25,459 --> 00:13:26,880
Now, I don't want to leave.

183
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:32,159
It's the same to die here or to die outside.

184
00:13:32,159 --> 00:13:35,340
I don't want to go out anymore. I'm not leaving.

185
00:13:47,400 --> 00:13:49,780
Why don't you say something?

186
00:13:49,780 --> 00:13:53,500
I'm afraid that I might upset you.

187
00:13:53,500 --> 00:13:55,159
What do you want me to say?

188
00:13:55,160 --> 00:13:57,720
Tell me why you are here.

189
00:13:57,720 --> 00:14:00,079
My apprentice caught me and brought me here.

190
00:14:00,080 --> 00:14:03,359
He imprisoned me here, but I don't know why.

191
00:14:04,140 --> 00:14:05,760
Apprentice?

192
00:14:05,760 --> 00:14:08,480
- Nanhai Crocodile?
- Yes!

193
00:14:09,360 --> 00:14:13,479
How about you, Sister Wan? Who caught you?

194
00:14:13,480 --> 00:14:17,640
I walked all the way from the palace to the riverside and ran into a weird old man.

195
00:14:17,640 --> 00:14:20,840
He is a cripple but his martial arts skills are incredible.

196
00:14:20,840 --> 00:14:22,540
I don't know what I did that offended him,

197
00:14:22,540 --> 00:14:24,920
then he locked me up in here.

198
00:14:25,704 --> 00:14:29,684
Does the emperor know where Wanjie Valley is?

199
00:14:29,684 --> 00:14:33,396
This is my first time hearing of this place. Wanjie Valley.

200
00:14:33,396 --> 00:14:38,840
I think it shouldn't be too far from the Dali Kingdom.

201
00:14:38,840 --> 00:14:40,860
You've heard what Gan Baobao said.

202
00:14:40,860 --> 00:14:44,020
I'm afraid that place can't be found easily.

203
00:14:44,020 --> 00:14:48,440
If Yu'er falls into the hands of the enemies for such a long time, I'm afraid...

204
00:14:48,440 --> 00:14:51,519
Yu'er has been spoiled as a kid and detached from worldly affairs.

205
00:14:51,519 --> 00:14:54,159
Let him suffer a bit of setback, experience some hardships.

206
00:14:54,160 --> 00:14:56,599
It might be a good thing for him.

207
00:14:56,600 --> 00:14:58,460
You don't have to worry about this matter.

208
00:14:58,460 --> 00:15:00,619
- But...
- Feng Huang'er,

209
00:15:00,619 --> 00:15:04,260
brother always regards Yu'er as his own child, he won't just sit back and do nothing.

210
00:15:04,260 --> 00:15:06,483
Feng Huang'er, don't be so worried.

211
00:15:06,483 --> 00:15:08,300
It's all because of you.

212
00:15:08,300 --> 00:15:10,320
If it wasn't for you,

213
00:15:10,320 --> 00:15:12,940
Yu'er wouldn't be in this situation.

214
00:15:12,940 --> 00:15:15,960
If anything happens to Yu'er,

215
00:15:15,960 --> 00:15:17,340
you...

216
00:15:18,520 --> 00:15:19,940
Feng Huang'er.

217
00:15:20,638 --> 00:15:22,340
I was at fault.

218
00:15:22,340 --> 00:15:25,740
Please rest assured. I will make sure Yu'er is safe and sound.

219
00:15:25,740 --> 00:15:28,380
Even if it means I have to risk my own life.

220
00:15:34,372 --> 00:15:36,080
Time to eat.

221
00:15:51,240 --> 00:15:52,560
Sister Wan.

222
00:16:01,780 --> 00:16:07,300
Sister Wan, do you think they would poison our food?

223
00:16:07,300 --> 00:16:08,940
Are you stupid?

224
00:16:09,840 --> 00:16:12,140
He's got such good martial arts that could kill us.

225
00:16:12,140 --> 00:16:14,220
Would he need to poison us to kill us?

226
00:16:15,980 --> 00:16:17,580
You're right.

227
00:16:35,800 --> 00:16:37,679
Sister Wan, don't worry.

228
00:16:37,680 --> 00:16:40,840
Uncle and Father will come to our rescue.

229
00:16:40,840 --> 00:16:43,340
Although Nanhai Crocodile and Second Madam Ye are highly skilled,

230
00:16:43,340 --> 00:16:45,839
they are definitely no match for Father and Uncle.

231
00:16:45,840 --> 00:16:47,980
Your uncle is just an emperor.

232
00:16:47,980 --> 00:16:49,439
How strong can he be?

233
00:16:49,440 --> 00:16:51,700
I don't believe he can defeat that green robe freak.

234
00:16:51,700 --> 00:16:56,619
The most he could do is bring along 2000 armored cavalry and attack.

235
00:16:56,619 --> 00:16:58,280
He won't.

236
00:16:58,280 --> 00:17:01,199
The ancestors of the Duan family are the warrior of the martial arts world.

237
00:17:01,200 --> 00:17:03,479
Although he is the Emperor of Dali,

238
00:17:03,480 --> 00:17:05,860
he dares not forget the rules in the martial arts world.

239
00:17:05,860 --> 00:17:09,279
If he abuses his power and attempts to win with a force superior in number,

240
00:17:09,280 --> 00:17:12,079
then he would be the joke of the heroes.

241
00:17:12,079 --> 00:17:18,620
Turns out the emperor or the prince has more rules to obey than those martial artists.

242
00:17:18,620 --> 00:17:23,619
My uncle used to say, never forget where you came from.

243
00:17:25,323 --> 00:17:30,223
A mouthful of benevolence and morality, but his ways of doing things are despicable.

244
00:17:32,600 --> 00:17:35,780
Your father already has your mother as his wife,

245
00:17:35,780 --> 00:17:38,320
and yet he does my master wrong.

246
00:17:40,180 --> 00:17:42,519
Sister Wan, how can you criticize my father?

247
00:17:42,520 --> 00:17:44,980
My father is your father, too.

248
00:17:44,980 --> 00:17:48,799
Moreover, look at all the princes and nobles in the world,

249
00:17:48,800 --> 00:17:51,040
which one of them doesn't have...

250
00:17:51,040 --> 00:17:54,040
All of them have a few...

251
00:17:55,700 --> 00:17:57,620
wives...

252
00:17:57,620 --> 00:17:59,020
I'm not calling him my father.

253
00:17:59,020 --> 00:18:02,320
A man who has many wives and concubines has no conscience.

254
00:18:04,300 --> 00:18:05,400
You're right.

255
00:18:05,400 --> 00:18:07,200
Sister Wan, you're right.

256
00:18:07,200 --> 00:18:09,540
I was too impetuous.

257
00:18:11,020 --> 00:18:14,720
But, Sister Wan, I need to tell you this.

258
00:18:14,720 --> 00:18:18,060
No matter what my father does, right or wrong, he is still my father.

259
00:18:18,060 --> 00:18:20,119
Moreover, he is your father too.

260
00:18:20,120 --> 00:18:21,479
You're his daughter.

261
00:18:21,480 --> 00:18:23,479
Then it makes me your elder brother.

262
00:18:23,480 --> 00:18:25,740
You can't be rude to Father.

263
00:18:25,740 --> 00:18:29,540
As your elder brother, I must teach you a lesson.

264
00:18:31,080 --> 00:18:34,600
To be double-minded is the same as being heartless.

265
00:18:38,480 --> 00:18:40,140
How can you hit your elder brother?

266
00:18:40,140 --> 00:18:42,080
How dare you dodge it?

267
00:18:44,660 --> 00:18:46,560
- Sister Wan.
- You...

268
00:18:50,160 --> 00:18:52,560
- Wan, Sister Wan.
- You...

269
00:18:55,860 --> 00:18:57,079
Sister Wan.

270
00:18:57,080 --> 00:18:58,480
You!

271
00:19:25,200 --> 00:19:27,140
You... What are you doing?

272
00:19:27,140 --> 00:19:29,460
You are my brother.

273
00:19:30,200 --> 00:19:32,740
I deserve to die!

274
00:19:34,160 --> 00:19:35,479
- Duan.
- Sister Wan.

275
00:19:35,480 --> 00:19:38,000
We seem to have fallen into someone else's trap.

276
00:19:39,720 --> 00:19:41,620
The food was poisoned.

277
00:19:45,100 --> 00:19:47,300
- Your Majesty.
- What's is it?

278
00:19:47,300 --> 00:19:50,680
Wanjie Valley is on the outskirts of the city, after crossing Shanrendu Town

279
00:19:50,680 --> 00:19:52,420
and the chain bridge, then we will arrive.

280
00:19:52,420 --> 00:19:54,660
However, the valley entrance is loaded with traps.

281
00:19:54,660 --> 00:19:56,600
I don't think we can get through it easily.

282
00:19:56,600 --> 00:19:58,819
- Get up.
- Thank you, Your Majesty.

283
00:19:58,819 --> 00:20:00,600
So you had plans earlier on, Your Majesty.

284
00:20:01,404 --> 00:20:03,555
I should have known that if Ba Sikong is going into action,

285
00:20:03,555 --> 00:20:06,855
there's no reason the enemy's hideout can remain a secret.

286
00:20:06,855 --> 00:20:09,799
And I wouldn't have to be worried for all this while.

287
00:20:09,800 --> 00:20:13,239
Your Highness, I'm flattered. Tian Shi dare not accept the compliment.

288
00:20:13,239 --> 00:20:14,739
- Ba Sikong.
- Here.

289
00:20:14,739 --> 00:20:16,780
Are the "Four Evils" in the valley?

290
00:20:16,780 --> 00:20:18,700
Your Majesty, they're in the valley.

291
00:20:18,700 --> 00:20:21,460
I have searched through the valley,

292
00:20:21,460 --> 00:20:23,740
but there was no sight of the young prince.

293
00:20:23,740 --> 00:20:26,420
However, I saw a man sending out meals to a stone house.

294
00:20:26,420 --> 00:20:30,080
They must be hiding the young prince in that room.

295
00:20:30,900 --> 00:20:33,300
Ba Sikong, you did a great job.

296
00:20:34,360 --> 00:20:35,820
Brother Chun.

297
00:20:36,800 --> 00:20:38,919
The "Four Evils" are highly skilled in martial arts.

298
00:20:38,920 --> 00:20:41,020
We must not spend too much time battling them.

299
00:20:41,020 --> 00:20:43,020
Our priority is to rescue Yu'er.

300
00:20:43,020 --> 00:20:44,640
Yes, Your Majesty.

301
00:20:46,400 --> 00:20:48,219
- Ba Sikong.
- Yes, Your Majesty.

302
00:20:48,219 --> 00:20:51,239
Next, take down what you've seen and heard, write and visualize them in detail.

303
00:20:51,239 --> 00:20:54,179
Tomorrow, bring along your people, we will set off for Wanjie Valley early in the morning.

304
00:20:54,179 --> 00:20:55,480
Yes, Your Majesty.

305
00:21:03,260 --> 00:21:05,320
Duan.

306
00:21:06,400 --> 00:21:12,980
Duan, I'm feeling hot. Duan.

307
