Duan, I still feel so hot.

308
00:21:29,860 --> 00:21:31,200
Duan.

309
00:21:31,200 --> 00:21:34,854
Sister Wan. Sister Wan.

310
00:21:35,760 --> 00:21:39,139
Lie on this stone bed, it can cool you down a bit.

311
00:21:57,480 --> 00:22:00,379
Sister Wan, lend me one of your poisoned arrows, please.

312
00:22:00,379 --> 00:22:01,559
What do you want to do?

313
00:22:01,560 --> 00:22:04,739
By the time the drug controls my sanity,

314
00:22:04,739 --> 00:22:07,740
I will use the poisoned arrow to jab myself to death.

315
00:22:07,740 --> 00:22:09,919
I must not hurt you!

316
00:22:09,920 --> 00:22:11,680
Don't.

317
00:22:11,680 --> 00:22:14,000
I can't bear to see you like this.

318
00:22:14,000 --> 00:22:18,100
How? Sister Wan, promise me.

319
00:22:18,100 --> 00:22:24,859
If I touch you in any form, you have to shoot me with the arrow immediately.

320
00:22:24,859 --> 00:22:26,820
No way. I can't do it.

321
00:22:26,820 --> 00:22:30,380
Sister Wan, I'm begging you. Please promise me.

322
00:22:30,380 --> 00:22:35,579
The centuries-old reputation of the Duan family cannot be ruined in my hands.

323
00:22:35,579 --> 00:22:40,299
If we do commit incest,

324
00:22:40,299 --> 00:22:43,779
how can I face the ancestors of the Duan family.

325
00:22:43,779 --> 00:22:46,820
Dali Duan family was extraordinary;

326
00:22:46,820 --> 00:22:49,519
however. after it fell into the hands of Duan Zhengming,

327
00:22:49,520 --> 00:22:51,614
a man who is nothing but a mouthful of benevolence and morality,

328
00:22:51,615 --> 00:22:54,479
deep inside he is cruel and unscrupulous.

329
00:22:54,480 --> 00:22:57,559
There's no more good reputation left of the family.

330
00:22:57,560 --> 00:23:00,800
Who are you? Who are you?

331
00:23:00,800 --> 00:23:02,479
You're talking nonsense!

332
00:23:02,480 --> 00:23:04,320
Duan.

333
00:23:04,320 --> 00:23:06,479
He's that weird old man.

334
00:23:06,480 --> 00:23:08,900
Miss Mu, you have my words.

335
00:23:08,900 --> 00:23:11,199
I can make your brother your husband.

336
00:23:11,200 --> 00:23:12,999
For sure, I will keep my promise.

337
00:23:13,000 --> 00:23:14,839
In the bowl of braised pork,

338
00:23:14,840 --> 00:23:18,420
I've put in a large amount of aphrodisiac.

339
00:23:18,420 --> 00:23:22,420
If you don't do it,

340
00:23:22,420 --> 00:23:27,039
your skin will crack and you'll bleed to death from the 7 orifices of the head.

341
00:23:27,040 --> 00:23:30,679
The drug efficacy will increase day by day.

342
00:23:30,680 --> 00:23:36,979
On the 8th day, even Da Luo God will find it hard to resist.

343
00:23:38,320 --> 00:23:40,050
Who on earth are you?

344
00:23:40,050 --> 00:23:43,750
There's no grudge between us. Why do you use such a deadly trap to harm me?

345
00:23:43,759 --> 00:23:46,719
How can I live my life without feeling ashamed then?

346
00:23:46,720 --> 00:23:49,759
You want to ruin my uncle's and my family's reputation.

347
00:23:49,760 --> 00:23:51,199
I would rather die a hundred times!

348
00:23:51,200 --> 00:23:54,399
I would rather die a hundred times than letting your conspiracy succeed!

349
00:23:54,400 --> 00:23:56,679
There's no grudge between us indeed,

350
00:23:56,680 --> 00:24:00,119
but there's deep resentment between your uncle and me.

351
00:24:00,120 --> 00:24:04,319
I want Duan Zhengchun and Duan Zhengming, these two brats to feel ashamed for the rest of their life.

352
00:24:04,319 --> 00:24:08,580
Even better, to be embarrassed about facing the public.

353
00:24:10,760 --> 00:24:13,720
Wonderful, wonderful.

354
00:24:25,500 --> 00:24:29,499
- Duan.
- Great, great.

355
00:24:29,499 --> 00:24:34,807
By the time both of you are married and have children, then I will release you.

356
00:24:34,807 --> 00:24:36,439
I'm not going to kill you;

357
00:24:36,440 --> 00:24:38,740
meanwhile, I'll pass my martial arts to both of you,

358
00:24:38,740 --> 00:24:41,300
to let both of you conquer the world.

359
00:24:41,300 --> 00:24:42,400
Don't even think about it!

360
00:24:42,400 --> 00:24:46,980
At the very last minute, I will kill myself by hitting my head on this stone wall.

361
00:24:46,980 --> 00:24:49,479
Sister Wan, please remember.

362
00:24:49,480 --> 00:24:52,740
The descendants of the Duan family would rather die than be humiliated.

363
00:24:52,740 --> 00:24:55,639
Dead or alive, that's not my concern.

364
00:24:55,640 --> 00:24:58,119
If you wish to kill yourself,

365
00:24:58,120 --> 00:25:02,399
I will strip your bodies naked, salt them,

366
00:25:02,400 --> 00:25:05,519
then hang them at the city center of Dali City for three days.

367
00:25:05,520 --> 00:25:09,959
I will make it clear that you are the nephew and niece of Dali Duan Zhengming,

368
00:25:09,960 --> 00:25:13,320
who committed adultery in private and got caught in the act.

369
00:25:13,320 --> 00:25:17,180
Both of you were too ashamed and thus committed suicide.

370
00:25:17,180 --> 00:25:19,740
Wouldn't it be better?

371
00:25:19,740 --> 00:25:24,820
How did the Dali Duan family offend you that

372
00:25:24,820 --> 00:25:27,799
you want to take such vicious revenge on us?

373
00:25:27,800 --> 00:25:31,479
I don't need to tell you my private matters.

374
00:25:31,480 --> 00:25:34,239
Siblings, hurry up and get things done,

375
00:25:34,240 --> 00:25:40,040
the sooner you give birth to a child, the sooner you can leave here.

376
00:26:11,310 --> 00:26:14,400
[Anyone with the last name Duan is not permitted in the valley]

377
00:26:23,220 --> 00:26:27,230
[Anyone with the last name Duan is not permitted and will be killed upon entrance]

378
00:26:27,780 --> 00:26:29,840
This Lord of the Wanjie Valley,

379
00:26:29,840 --> 00:26:33,980
how much resentment does he hold against the Duan family?

380
00:26:44,830 --> 00:26:46,090
[Anyone with the last name... ]

381
00:26:47,980 --> 00:26:49,880
Let's go!

382
00:27:23,940 --> 00:27:28,959
The brothers of the Dali Kingdom Duan family are here to pay an official visit.
[Visiting Card]

383
00:28:04,760 --> 00:28:06,640
Hey, Duans!

384
00:28:06,640 --> 00:28:09,820
If you're visiting and abiding by the rules of the martial arts world,

385
00:28:09,820 --> 00:28:12,220
why did you break the valley's entrance?

386
00:28:17,420 --> 00:28:19,180
Where is my son?

387
00:28:19,180 --> 00:28:22,040
Where did you guys hide him?

388
00:28:31,620 --> 00:28:33,180
You're late.

389
00:28:33,180 --> 00:28:34,879
That Duan boy?

390
00:28:34,880 --> 00:28:38,260
We had cut his body open and fed the dogs.

391
00:28:38,260 --> 00:28:39,932
I'm asking Lord Zhong.

392
00:28:39,932 --> 00:28:43,992
I'm not talking to you, a commoner woman.

393
00:29:03,440 --> 00:29:05,460
Wait a minute!

394
00:29:10,360 --> 00:29:11,860
Stop fighting.

395
00:29:11,860 --> 00:29:14,100
Duan Zhengchun!

396
00:29:46,480 --> 00:29:47,480
Feng Huang'er.

397
00:29:47,480 --> 00:29:49,660
I don't need your help.

398
00:29:58,500 --> 00:30:02,060
Feng Huang'er, don't be so relentless.

399
00:30:02,060 --> 00:30:03,860
What's with the phoenix and peacock?
(TN: Feng Huang means 'phoenix' in Chinese)

400
00:30:03,860 --> 00:30:06,300
Calling her with such affection.

401
00:30:22,660 --> 00:30:24,220
Husband.

402
00:30:26,200 --> 00:30:27,500
Why did you kick my husband?

403
00:30:27,500 --> 00:30:29,690
Duan, I didn't mean to do that.

404
00:30:29,690 --> 00:30:31,240
Are you all right?

405
00:30:53,280 --> 00:30:54,540
Stop!

406
00:30:54,540 --> 00:30:55,960
Fight him!

407
00:31:08,303 --> 00:31:12,103
Duan thief! You're such a boy toy!

408
00:31:12,103 --> 00:31:16,560
All you do is rely on women to save your life, are you a true man or not?

409
00:31:40,360 --> 00:31:42,360
You're not injured!

410
00:31:42,360 --> 00:31:46,460
This guy is good at deceiving people, and yet you trust him.

411
00:31:47,640 --> 00:31:49,100
Take this!

412
00:31:53,180 --> 00:31:56,980
What a sin.

413
00:32:15,540 --> 00:32:17,260
Yes, Your Majesty.

414
00:33:23,440 --> 00:33:26,540
You are my biological sons. How could you attack your mother?

415
00:33:26,540 --> 00:33:29,279
Aren't you afraid of being punished by God's lightning strikes?

416
00:33:29,280 --> 00:33:32,340
You witch! You are full of nonsense. Take this!

417
00:33:42,480 --> 00:33:45,020
You bastard!

418
00:34:27,980 --> 00:34:30,720
Sir, please let me through.

419
00:34:38,819 --> 00:34:41,460
If you won't let me through,

420
00:34:41,460 --> 00:34:44,420
then don't blame me for being rude.

421
00:35:37,280 --> 00:35:41,160
Your staff skill is the same origin as the Duan family's One-finger Death Touch.

422
00:35:41,160 --> 00:35:45,920
Are you related to the Duan family?

423
00:35:45,920 --> 00:35:50,320
Are you Duan Zhengming or Duan Zhengchun?

424
00:35:50,320 --> 00:35:53,460
I'm Duan Zhengming.

425
00:35:57,160 --> 00:35:58,760
Uncle.

426
00:36:00,480 --> 00:36:01,720
Uncle.

427
00:36:05,340 --> 00:36:08,060
So you're the Emperor Baoding?

428
00:36:08,060 --> 00:36:11,079
Compare your martial arts skills to mine.

429
00:36:11,080 --> 00:36:13,520
Whose are better?

430
00:36:14,855 --> 00:36:18,735
If we talk about martial arts skills, you're slightly better than me.

431
00:36:18,735 --> 00:36:21,180
However, if we were to fight,

432
00:36:21,180 --> 00:36:25,720
I can assure you that I can defeat you.

433
00:36:27,580 --> 00:36:29,120
Not bad.

434
00:36:29,120 --> 00:36:34,160
After all, I'm at a disadvantage of physical disability.

435
00:36:34,160 --> 00:36:37,460
After years of holding the title of emperor,

436
00:36:37,460 --> 00:36:42,840
