443
00:37:06,440 --> 00:37:08,620
Aphrodisiac?

444
00:37:08,620 --> 00:37:10,620
What kind of drug is that?

445
00:37:10,620 --> 00:37:13,140
It's not a drug.

446
00:37:13,140 --> 00:37:17,520
It's just a type of powerful aphrodisiac.

447
00:37:17,520 --> 00:37:24,159
Don't you know there's a woman in the stone house?

448
00:37:42,200 --> 00:37:46,519
