449
00:37:46,520 --> 00:37:51,140
That'll add to your sins.

450
00:38:03,740 --> 00:38:05,880
Why are you doing this to our Duan family?

451
00:38:05,880 --> 00:38:08,880
Who are you?

452
00:38:18,340 --> 00:38:21,440
I'm the former crown prince of Dali Kingdom,

453
00:38:21,440 --> 00:38:24,000
Duan Yanqing.

454
00:38:33,620 --> 00:38:35,340
I don't believe you.

455
00:39:14,240 --> 00:39:19,740
