456
00:39:23,220 --> 00:39:26,360
Zhengming greets Senior.

457
00:39:27,940 --> 00:39:32,159
You address me as a senior. Is it because you refuse to recognize me?

458
00:39:32,160 --> 00:39:36,260
Or are you still having a doubt?

459
00:39:37,840 --> 00:39:42,539
As the head of a country, I must take extra caution in my words and deeds.

460
00:39:43,320 --> 00:39:47,400
Senior, I don't have an heir.

461
00:39:47,400 --> 00:39:52,040
Yu'er is entrusted with the sustenance of the ancestral temple and sacred shrine.

462
00:39:52,040 --> 00:39:56,480
Senior, let them go.

463
00:40:00,800 --> 00:40:03,559
